Package org.universAAL.ri.gateway.proxies

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ProxyBusMember
    Generic interface for any proxy representing any imported or exported BusMember, independently of the bus they associate to.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BusMemberReference
    An identifier of a concrete BusMember across all Scopes.
    ProxyBusMemberFactory
    Factory to create Proxies.
    ProxyPool
    A place holder for all ProxyBusMembers.
    ReferencesManager
    Utility class to help ProxyBusMembers to manage their references.
